 his first New York gallery show, at the Jack Shainman Gallery; became a professor at the School of Art and Design at the University of Illinois at Chicago (1998); explored social and political issues in the comic book RythmMastr; honors include, the Alpert Award in the Arts, MacArthur Foundation's Fellows Program grant (1997))00561cz  a2200145n  4500001001300000003000400013005001700017008004100034010001700075040002300092110001900115410002800134410009500162670015800257n  00000505 DLC20000121141001.0000121n| acannaabn          |a ana        an  00000505   aDLCbengcDLCdDLC2 aCOSALC Project2 aUnesco.bCOSALC Project2 aUniversity of Puerto Rico (Mayagüez campus).bSea Grant College Program.bCOSALC Project  aCoast and beach stability ... 1998:bt.p. (COSALC Project) p. 1 (jointly sponsored by Unesco and the University of Puerto Rico Sea Grant College Program)00428nz  a2200121n  4500001001300000003000400013005001700017008004100034010001700075040001800092110006400110670013200174n  00001100 DLC20000215092126.0000215n| acannaabn          |n ana        an  00001100   aDLCbengcDLC2 aUniversity of Reading.bCouncil for Environmental Education  aDearling, Alan. Youth action and the environment, 1997bt.p. verso (Council for Environmental Education, University of Reading)01713cz  a2200361n  n  00001559 DLC20191023073148.0000202n| azannaabn          |a aaa        an  00001559   a(OCoLC)oca05147316  aDLCbengerdacDLCdCStdTxU-Da  f1960-05-192edtf1 aKehtarnavaz, Nasser  eBryan (Tex.)2naf  ePlano (Tex.)2naf  fHouston (Tex.)2naf  fCollege Station (Tex.)2naf  fRichardson (Tex.)2naf  aSignal processing2lcsh  aMachine learning2lcsh  aRice University2naf  aTexas A & M University2naf  aUniversity of Texas at Dallas2naf  aUniversity and college faculty members2lcdgt  aMales2lcdgt  aeng2 wriGraduate of:aRice University2 wriEmployer:aTexas A & M University2 wriEmployer:aUniversity of T